ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: Absolutely. One of the best graduate seminars I have ever taken.
Highly recommended, especially for those interested in the origins of theater.

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
comments: Excellent preparation. I would have appreciated more secondary readings.

Nearly every play read is either on our reading list or is by an author who is on the reading list; in addition this course led me to consider theater as a genre more closely in my studies of literature.
